</p>

<ul>
    <li>email adress</li>
    <li>user name</li>
    <li>secure hash of your password</li>
    <li>Switch account name (optional)</li>
    <li>Switch friend code (optional)</li>
    <li>name of your Animal Crossing New Horizons villager (optional)</li>
    <li>name of your Animal Crossing New Horizons island (optional)</li>
