<p>
    Cookies are used to store your identity when logged in. This way you don't have to login each time, when visiting this site.
</p>

<p>
    Again, <b>no</b> data is shared with any third party and is only used to provide the services of this site. In addition you can see and delete any personal data through
    the acccount page. Thes source code of this page can be found on GitHub <a href="https://github.com/kuper-adrian/TurnipExchange">here</a>.
</p>

<p>
    To ensure a secure and private connection, this site is only reachable via HTTPS using an SSL certificate provided by Lets Encrypt. The server is hosted by Digital Ocean
